<h1>Payment Confirmation</h1>
<p>Dear <%= @user.name %>,</p>
<p>Thank you for your payment. Your order <strong>#<%= @order.id %></strong> has been successfully processed.</p>
<p><strong>Order Details:</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li>Order Date: <%= @order.order_date %></li>
  <li>Total Amount: <%= number_to_currency(@order.total_amount, unit: "", format: "%n BDT") %></li>
  <li>Payment Status: <%= @order.payment.payment_status.titleize %></li>
</ul>
<p>You can review your order at any time by visiting your account.</p>
<p>Best regards,</p>
<p>The WellShopping Team</p>
